The band played its first show during their high school graduation ceremomy in 1999. {{cite web | work = Lunkhead.jp title = Lunkhead Biography year = 2004 url = | http://www.lunkhead.jp/profile/index.html accessdate = 2007-09-22 }} Lunkhead officially became a band when all four members reunited in Tokyo in 2000. On 2 February 2009, drummer Ishikawa Ryou announced on the band's official website of his departure from the band in April 2009. {{cite web | work = Lunkhead.jp title = Staff Special year = 2009 url = | http://lunkhead.jp/staff/index.html accessdate = 2009-02-03 }}
